# Project Documentation

At the start of every conversation, read these two files before doing any work:

1. `ARCHITECTURE.MD` — system design, invariants, key types, and how the components fit together
2. `DEBUGGING_GUIDE.md` — how to build (`./cb.sh`), run tests (`./ct.sh`), and debug failures

Always use `./cb.sh` and `./ct.sh` for building and testing. Never use `cargo test` directly.
